Package jioc.annotation

Contains annotation support and data structures required for AnnotationApplicationConfig to implement dependency injection.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotatedPea<T>
    The main data structure for storing a component annotated by @Pea.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    AutoInject
    Marks a field as to be auto injected by the JIOC dependency injection mechanism.
    Pea
    Indicates that the annotated class should be managed by the JIOC framework and is considered as a candidate for auto-detection when using annotation-based configuration.
